descriptionNullable:
### Context

This dataset contains annotated cars in .xml format , it can be used for computer vision or deep learning projects.


### Content

The dataset contains 269 samples (images with their annotations) for training folder , and 57 samples for test folder.
The number_of_samples.csv file contains the number of samples info in each directory.
random images were selected , all have random angles and sizes in order to give as much variety for the model to train as possible.


### Inspiration

This is for a continuous project i am currently working on out of passion ,hope you like it.
